1. Cilantro Sauce 
    Ingredients: 
        - 1 cilantro bush
        - garlic cloves
        - plain greek yoghurt
        - 2 limes juiced
        - salt and pepper to taste
       
    *Food processor 

2. Pesto Sauce 
    Ingredients:
         - pine nuts
        - basil
        - evoo
        - garlic cloves
        - salt and pepper to taste 
               
    *Food processor 

3. Green Goddess Dressing 
    Ingredients: 
        - avocado
        - basil
        - cilantro 
        - plain greek yoghurt 
        - 2 pinches fresh dill 
        - 1 lemon juied 
        - garlic cloves
        - cumin
        - salt and pepper to taste

    *Food processor 

4. Garlic Sauce 
    Ingredients: 
        - 1 cup garlic cloves 
        - 3 cups neautral oil (ex. grapeseed oil)
        - 1/2 cup lemon juiced
        - 1 1/12 tbsp coarse salt

    *Food processor 


